Accessibility Options
General Settings
  Set Player Speed (Slider?) - Speed up or slow down the player’s speed.
  Find a set floor and ceiling in order to allow users to move at a speed that feels right to them.
  Teleportation Enabled? [Bool] - Swap to standard movement (or just disable the teleport button)
  Music [Bool] - Turn music on/off
  Volume [Slider 0-100] - Change the volume of the music
  Camera Sensitivity [Slider] - Change how sensitive the camera is on Mouse and Keyboard
  Reset Location [Character Stuck] - OPTIONAL, just a thought though…

Accessibility Settings
  Rotating Skybox [Bool] - Turn skybox rotation on/off
  FOV [Slider] - Change the field of view for the camera
  Fadeout Timer [Slider] - Change how long the fadeout time animation is between teleportations.
  Auto-Shuffle Art [Bool] - Turn on/off the auto shuffling art
  Enhanced Text [Bool] - Make the text always the larger size
  Enable Subtitles [Bool] - This is a stretch, and may not be possible, but could be useful
  Enable Vignette [Bool] - Turn Vignette on/off 
  Accessibility Presets (Low/Med/High) - Might have some defaults that enable or disable certain things
  Enhanced Interaction [Bool] - Increases the size of hitboxes to make interacting easier
